法嫁<br />\n慢慢跟住大隊走就完"},{"pid":"b0b41ea6a7ac5710ff981b8d982b06c0e0ae4b2d","tid":1454923,"uid":34429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:31:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211b43a5aed63d4b6ca4ad61869c893395a4182a","tid":1454923,"uid":24697,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:31:20.000Z","msg":"都冇旅客<br />\n機已停<br />\n留係機場做乜<br />\n不分化，但通知在場人士"},{"pid":"37f09abb7294c99420717f515f00d33eebbf6016","tid":1454923,"uid":71237,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:31:44.000Z","msg":"唔需要戀戰。<br />\n應該日日去機場，等佢日日都取消航班。<br />\n<br />\n而家機管局主動配合玩不合作運動，瘋狂取消航班有用過地鐵阻塞車門100倍啦。"},{"pid":"66163db8a75a7bbc865ca7a8037f5740b3f077f8","tid":1454923,"uid":249347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9b29a5b3d7098bdbd3a9d2f802f0bd704345166f","tid":1454923,"uid":34429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:29:32.000Z","msg":"空群而出叫人散水嘅，其實有幾多個喺現場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:31:44.000Z","msg":"一陣記得帶頭衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPS 我講衝去廁所"},{"pid":"7b75a958a40d79cc2e1ff339d532a56d3133c406","tid":1454923,"uid":34429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9351c675a892e916c7cf50f1565bf7fff747c31e","tid":1454923,"uid":50327,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:31:56.000Z","msg":"唔散, D 臥底就會藉機搞事入我地數<br />\n散, 聽日仲可以繼續, 最好再停飛"},{"pid":"e2f4b4b3aa66161cb14f8fb22fbb7fae3bd82507","tid":1454923,"uid":291491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:32:08.000Z","msg":"去定留自己決定"},{"pid":"4ce94af729fdd28489c6023a52a9b8195001bc0d","tid":1454923,"uid":52939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:32:12.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"4a6bb9ac2e57c2822afe8e4a87e83c203c6ea486","tid":1454923,"uid":34429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:32:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b55dffab42f68bc4b9db7573d677a79923d53b7a","tid":1454923,"uid":44358,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:32:22.000Z","msg":"1.) 集會冇經批准，佢要咬你冇佢乎。<br />\n2.) 依家擺明封機場（停晒升降），準備大屠殺。<br />\n3.) 出事時，你係機場，根本冇路可以走。<br />\n<br />\n睇飛機升降日日有，明天請早啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想再有巴絲受傷呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41df0775d19d63ffaac54cb7d62e77ed6da6c54e","tid":1454923,"uid":5475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:32:35.000Z","msg":"你自己留啦 屌你老母<br />\n目標達成仲唔走等比狗爆頭?"},{"pid":"fd61fda259487b561c82ebe43a56f50776d6196d","tid":1454923,"uid":34429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:32:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a5d216485b6b652d03c12215de0daa91734aabc","tid":1454923,"uid":294318,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:33:12.000Z","msg":"老規矩, 現場事現場決定"},{"pid":"77bf6c2815706c2fb1331e03ecf41f3ffa81f417","tid":1454923,"uid":114801,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:33:18.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n728交哂比現場，好撚後悔"},{"pid":"6b3370d33d28580cc501812d2613e20a7f1267f7","tid":1454923,"uid":257109,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"41df0775d19d63ffaac54cb7d62e77ed6da6c54e","tid":1454923,"uid":5475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:32:35.000Z","msg":"你自己留啦 屌你老母<br />\n目標達成仲唔